Subject: Potential File Transfer Speed Throttling
Description: A colleague was transferring a large number of files to USB storage as part of an investigation. They received a pop-up alert for hitting the daily file transfer limit (which is in monitor-only mode) then commented their file transfer speed has significantly decreased after getting this pop-up. I'll attach their computer's EPP logs ASAP.
Solution_Comment__c: Issue was resolved by disabling the file transfer threshold
